articles.title: China's Great Wall damaged by workers looking for shortcut - BBC
articles.description: Part of the wall running through China's Shanxi province was dug open, causing severe damage.
articles.content:
A part of China's Great Wall has been severely damaged by construction workers in central Shanxi province, who used an excavator to dig through it.
